QuestData.Title: Building Our Arsenal
QuestData.Description:
Our fight against the faithless is an uphill battle we're bound to lose. We are outnumbered and out armed.
What few weapons we have aren't enough to outfit the entire temple.
With a few more spears and daggers, we might stand a chance fighting them off until our loa can be returned to us.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Sethrak Weapons from within the Temple Incursion.
